        <div class="form-container">
            <div class="title-head grey">
                WHAT IS FAIR TRADE?
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="title-head">
            <div class="header-copy">
            <p>
                 Wikipedia's definition of Fair Trade is : "an organized social movement and market-based approach that aims to help producers in developing countries make better trading conditions and promote sustainability. The movement advocates the payment of a higher price to producers as well as higher social and environmental standards. It focuses in particular on exports from developing countries to developed countries, most notably handicrafts, coffee, cocoa, sugar, tea, bananas, honey, cotton, wine, fresh fruit, chocolate, flowers, and gold."            
             </p>

            <p>
              Helping farmers who grow and process the cocoa, sugar, chocolate and vanilla we use is of paramount importance to us. If they are paid and treated fairly and able to practice sustainable and healthy farming practices, then we are sure to see continued production.           
             </p>

            </div>
        </div>


